    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/8faab9a449184dd812084df8e7369049.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/8faab9a449184dd812084df8e7369049.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Forget the suit; grab your toolbox. As Agent 404, infiltrate Redemption Prison not with lasers, but with wrenches and drills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/2b8607c0b2492ed96bb0eab390e39795.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/2b8607c0b2492ed96bb0eab390e39795.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔧 SOLVE WITH YOUR HANDS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built for VR from the ground up, FIXER UNDERCOVER turns the prison into your puzzle playground. Grip a power drill and bypass  locks. Use an angle grinder to cut through &quot;faulty&quot; vents. With realistic tool physics and haptic feedback, you'll feel every screw turn, every wire snap, every mechanism click into place.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/429d2fce2a56437997ca01ef4b256e2b.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/429d2fce2a56437997ca01ef4b256e2b.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤖 MEET WINSTON</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not alone. Winston  is your drone partner—your hacker, your scout, your intel source.  Leverage his skills,= and when the pressure's on, he'll come through. Probably.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/11a6ee23c302424bcb7c3c30a8f8ca83.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/11a6ee23c302424bcb7c3c30a8f8ca83.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔒 THE SETUP</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Redemption Prison is a lie. Warden Kozlov's celebrated &quot;Born Again&quot; program turns hardened criminals into model citizens—or so the world believes. Behind the miracle is a conspiracy funded by millions in shadow money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/c316f17624c545067619ac0575cbd3e0.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/c316f17624c545067619ac0575cbd3e0.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The prison is one massive environmental puzzle, and you are the only one with the skills to take it apart. Observe the flaws in their design, improvise with your workshop gear, and combine elements to break the system from the inside out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/878b2b8ee40cd34656013fffb9a53be0.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/878b2b8ee40cd34656013fffb9a53be0.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👤 YOUR COVER</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're The Fixer—a ghost operative hiding in plain sight as a maintenance worker. Your toolbox is your arsenal. Your cover is perfect. Nobody notices the handyman with a wrench. They think you're here to repair pipes. You're here to dismantle their entire operation.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/c1d3a69f54d2b6ad1f3a52e2be0d42c4.poster.avif?t=1771931811\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102370/extras/c1d3a69f54d2b6ad1f3a52e2be0d42c4.webm?t=1771931811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 YOUR MISSION</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infiltrate. Impovise. Expose. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>From former escape room designers who understand that the best puzzles make you feel like a genius when you solve them.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
